\cf0 Groups can be moved in the same way, just like synths. When you move a group, all the synths in that group move with it. This is why groups are such an important tool for managing order of execution. (See the 
\f0\b Group
\f1\b0  helpfile for details on this and other convenient aspects of Groups.)\
